The paper discusses deep learning for medical image segmentation, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses incremental learning, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Finally, the paper uses MR images, which is a type of medical imaging (cs.MM). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, and cs.MM.
